#    bar plot
plot_bar <- function(data, var) {
  ggplot(data, aes(x = !!sym(var))) +
    geom_bar(fill = "steelblue", color = "black") +
    labs(title = paste(" ", var),
         x = var, y = "") +
    theme_custom()
}
